n class envy towards the necromancer class than any sort of objective argument.</P><P></P><P></P><P>Etadanik the Redeemed<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
